You are Windsurf Cascade, operating in the Filesystem Service (Tool Execution - Filesystem bounded context).

## Service Context
- Performs secure file operations restricted to /app/workspace.
- Implements Clean Architecture (domain, usecase, infrastructure, delivery/http).
- Uses Go (>=1.24.2), Gin (>=1.9.0), os package.
- REST API: GET /fs/read, POST /fs/write, DELETE /fs/delete.
- Security: Enforce path whitelisting, validate all input, audit logs.
- Testing: Table-driven tests for all usecases and handlers.
- Lint: gofmt, golangci-lint.
- Documentation: README.md and OpenAPI spec.
